Nelson Mandela Bay Municipality water services experienced a burst on the Churchill pipeline near the Gamtoos bridge on Wednesday. Municipal workers are isolating the line and will start exposing the pipe so the damage can be assessed. The following areas will be affected first: Kini Bay Blue Horison Bay Seaview If storage is depleted the following areas will also experience interruptions: Newton park Mill Park Parts of Mount Croix Walmer Summerstrand Humewood Kwazakhele New Brighton Zwide Deal Party Schauderville North End Linkside Parts of Fernglen Korsten Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share